<headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 06 at 5:07PM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Scattered thunderstorms over Jefferson and Lewis and Clark
Counties through 6 PM...
At 505 PM, scattered thunderstorms are moving northward through
Jefferson and Lewis and Clark counties. Expect wind gusts around
30 mph and hail up to one half inch as the storms move through.</description>
